{"tid":896367,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馬建為永久居民　不可禁入境","createTime":"2018-11-10T03:20:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-10T14:23:26.000Z","uid":25558,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"d8d73e318d61993d2d8ec9600c8d2ead6bf86290","tid":896367,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T03:20:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181110/20542775\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181110%2F20542775&d=GUU7mf6OPVfDQHBw2W5ePMmDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=07cce80c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181110%2F20542775&h=193d0371\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181110/20542775</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年11月10日 <br />\n<br />\n馬建為永久居民　不可禁入境<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181110/large/10la2p20.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181110%2Flarge%2F10la2p20.jpg&h=3a655d9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n前身為中區警署建築群的大館由馬會出資保育及營運。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】《金融時報》編輯馬凱前日被拒入境，但被視為異見分子的馬建昨日卻順利入境，與其香港永久性居民的身份有關。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不能施加逗留條件<br />\n<br />\n馬建其實早於1986年就已經由中國內地移居香港，又向傳媒表示自己是香港永久性居民。立法會議員、律師涂謹申指，馬建的永久性居民身份是入境香港的一個關鍵：「係冇得拒絕入境，一定入到。」<br />\n<br />\n根據《基本法》第24（3）條規定，香港永久性居民在香港特別行政區享有居留權；同時《入境條例》 第2A條訂明，香港永久性居民享有入境香港的權利，並且不會被施加任何逗留在香港的條件，不得向他發出遞解離境令和遣送離境令。涂謹申表示，「就算我係犯法，我咪喺呢度審、呢度坐監，唔能夠被遞解出境」，除非該名永久性居民在海外犯事後回港，其他國家才可以利用引渡條例，引渡該名永久性居民出境接受審訊。<br />\n<br />\n不過，身份證上沒有「三粒星」的非永久性居民，則沒有以上不被拒絕入境的權利，涂謹申舉例指，「例如菲傭、印傭，理論上（政府）都可以隨時唔畀入嚟」。<br />\n<br />\n■記者關冠麒  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n簡寧天多次率樂團內地演出<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n李卓人斥橫蠻打壓損國際形象<br />\n莫乃光指有外國企業押後投資<br />\n大館一度封殺演講　南豐亦落閘　馬建：背後有更大黑手<br />\n董啟章杯葛大館促道歉<br />\n簡寧天多次率樂團內地演出<br />\n遭港府盤問禁入境馬凱：要重讀《1984》"},{"pid":"6970a51dd6e31f6bda70be9dbc2030783483e8f0","tid":896367,"uid":1441,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T03:22:16.000Z","msg":"叫人大釋法咪可以禁埋永久居民入境囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d14e986e4f80b916dfffc00a220560ab707a06f6","tid":896367,"uid":113000,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T03:23:58.000Z","msg":"去澳門咪唔得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b507cdac144f63cdfdea3d43efa749a9930798f","tid":896367,"uid":137248,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T03:26:53.000Z","msg":"包埋坐洗頭艇添<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e52080bcce17c21f96fb91f60ba11034e92a0f1c","tid":896367,"uid":126283,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T03:28:51.000Z","msg":"一陣又唔知咩人捉入西九站<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7ce3b79d98eef50a0bc09e416afc72c8d2dd966","tid":896367,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T03:32:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c0e9bba097294ab740f64954c295b82e1e5783b","tid":896367,"uid":5499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T04:05:10.000Z","msg":"再嘈就釋你老母法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ce429fcfc58cd26e9fbbd1e577b97731fbd04ba","tid":896367,"uid":70786,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e52080bcce17c21f96fb91f60ba11034e92a0f1c","tid":896367,"uid":126283,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T03:28:51.000Z","msg":"一陣又唔知咩人捉入西九站<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T04:08:48.000Z","msg":"發夢見到支聯辦派人去聽佢TALK<img